                <h1>Do Pending Charges Appear on Background Checks?</h1>
                <p>Pending charges may show up on a background check, depending on the type of check conducted. Standard checks often reveal criminal records, and if charges are recent, they could be included. It's important to note that not all background checks are the same; some may only reflect convictions, while others can include pending charges.</p>
